rent font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">About</p></a><a href="../projects"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Projects</p></a><a href="../insights"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Insights</p></a><a href="../contact"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl leading-none hover:text-yellow transition-colors">Contact</p></a></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit col-span-full pb-8 border-l border-current pl-unit pt-unit h-full"><div class="col-span-6 pr-6"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Bolt Builds is a design, build, and fabrication firm located in Greenpoint, Brooklyn.</p><div class="pt-4"><a class="block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=202+Banker+Street+Brooklyn+NY+11222"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">202 Banker Street</p><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">Brooklyn, NY 11222</p></a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@bolt.build">hello@bolt.build</a><a class="text-current font-body text-xl block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="tel:+1 917-740-3463">+1 917-740-3463</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 border-t-0 lg:border-t border-x md:border-x-0 border-current"></div></div></div><div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10"><div class="cover-image-shim absolute inset-0 z-10"></div><img src="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcSet="https://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=1920&q=75amp;qhttps://www.boltdesign.nyc/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F4j6lg3tu%2Fproduction%2F52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg&w=3840&q=75;w=3840&amp;q=75 2x" alt="Bar Design NYC, Bolt, Bolt Builds, Bolt Builds NYC, Bolt Builds New York City, Bolt Design NYC, Bolt New York City, Boutique Design Agency New York, Custom Interior Design New York, Custom millwork NYC, Elegant Hospitality Interiors NYC, High-End Bar Design NYC, High-End Interior Design Agency NYC, High-End Retail Design New York, High-end Millwork NYC, Hospitality, Hospitality Interior Design New York, Innovative Hospitality Solutions New York, Luxery Millwork NYC, Luxury Bar Design NYC, Luxury Hospitality Consultants NYC, Luxury Millwork NYC, NYC Residential Interior Designers, New York, New York City, New York Design and Branding for Hospitality, New York Hospitality Branding, New York Retail Interior Design, Sophisticated Branding Agency NYC, luxury Hospitality Design NYC" width="1447" height="859" class="absolute object-cover w-full h-full z-0 inset-0" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 300vw, (max-width: 1000px) 200vw, 100vw"/></div><div class="border-x flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end"></div></header><div class="z-20 relative bg-white"><div class="sticky top-0 invisible"><div class="px-unit absolute left-0 right-0 bg-white"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-b"></div></div></div><div class="px-unit"><div class="pt-unit border-black border-x"><div class="sticky top-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-2 pb-4"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3 pr-2"><p class="text-current font-body text-3xl">Assistant Project Manager</p></div><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-2"><h3 class="text-current font-body text-md">February 4, 2026</h3></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit pt-8 pb-unit"><div class="col-start-1 col-end-13 md:col-start-2 md:col-end-12 lg:col-start-4 lg:col-end-12 xl:col-start-4 xl:col-end-10"><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>About Bolt</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is a full-service <strong>Design + Build</strong> firm and fully insured <strong>General Contractor</strong> based in Brooklyn. We specialize in design-forward hospitality, retail, and residential projects that merge classical sensibility with innovative construction and fabrication methods. We believe that great design is only as strong as its execution — and that means being just as rigorous about budgets, schedules, and communication as we are about creative vision.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>The Role</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">Bolt is seeking an <strong>Assistant Project Manager</strong> to support construction operations across hospitality, retail, and residential projects. This is an ideal role for someone early-to-mid career who is eager to grow within a <strong>design-build</strong> environment and learn the full lifecycle of a project — from preconstruction through closeout.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">You’ll work closely with Construction Project Managers, Designers, and site teams to help keep projects on track, on budget, and well-coordinated. This role blends office-based coordination with regular site involvement and is well-suited for someone highly organized, proactive, and ready to take ownership of details.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Support Senior Project Managers with <strong>budget tracking, cost coding, and invoice review</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Assist in maintaining <strong>project schedules</strong>, updating timelines and flagging potential conflicts or delays</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Coordinate subcontractors, vendors, and internal teams to ensure smooth day-to-day project execution</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Help prepare bid packages, review subcontractor proposals, and assist with bid leveling</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Track and document <strong>change orders</strong>, RFIs, and submittals</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Maintain organized project files, meeting notes, and documentation across active jobs</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Participate in site visits, punch walks, and inspections as needed</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Assist with permitting coordination and inspections (DOB, FDNY, etc.) under PM guidance</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Communicate clearly and professionally with internal teams, consultants, and subcontractors</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Support continuous improvement of Bolt’s project management systems and workflows</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>2–5 years of experience</strong> in construction or project management, ideally within a design-build, GC, or interiors-focused firm</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Strong interest in <strong>construction operations, scheduling, and cost management</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Familiarity with construction drawings and basic building systems</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Proficiency (or willingness to learn quickly) in tools such as <strong>Bluebeam, Excel, and project management software</strong></li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Highly organized, detail-oriented, and dependable</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Comfortable juggling multiple tasks and priorities in a fast-paced environment</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Clear written and verbal communication skills</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Collaborative mindset with a willingness to ask questions and learn from senior team members</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4">Interest in growing into a <strong>full Project Manager role</strong> over time</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Why Bolt</strong></p><ul class="space-y-2"><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>See your work built — and built fast.</strong> At Bolt, you won’t be stuck pushing paper for years before seeing results. Our projects move quickly, and the work you put in becomes something real, tangible, and lasting.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Be hands-on.</strong> You won’t be siloed behind a screen — you’ll be in the field, in meetings, on walk-throughs, and fully involved in the process from start to finish.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work in the heart of Greenpoint.</strong> Our studio is based in one of Brooklyn’s most creative neighborhoods — surrounded by great food, inspiring spaces, and a thriving design community.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Join a company on the rise.</strong> Bolt is entering a new chapter of growth — and we’re building something special. You’ll help shape the future of the company, not just execute the present.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Build projects you’re proud of.</strong> From thoughtful restaurants to bold retail environments, you’ll be part of a team that sweats the details and cares deeply about design, craft, and execution.</li><li class="list-disc list-outside ml-4"><strong>Work with good people.</strong> We’re a tight-knit, driven team that takes pride in what we do — and has fun doing it. We value trust, accountability, and creative problem-solving.</li></ul><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4"><strong>Compensation</strong></p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">This is a full-time, in-person role based in our <strong>Greenpoint, Brooklyn</strong> studio.</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md mb-4">The base salary range for this position is <strong>$65,000–$80,000</strong>, depending on experience and qualifications. Bolt also offers performance-based bonus opportunities and clear pathways for advancement into a Project Manager role.</p><div class="mt-16 pb-12"><div class="px-6 py-8 bg-faint text-center"><p class="text-current font-body text-xl">To apply for this job, please email your resume to<!-- --> <a href="mailto:hello@bolt.build" class="font-bold hover:text-blue transition-colors border-b border-current border-dotted">hello@bolt.build ↗</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><footer class="bg-white pb-unit px-unit relative z-[1000]"><div class="bg-white border border-b border-black pt-unit pb-unit"><div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-unit px-unit"><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-3"><a class="text-current hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="../index.html"><div class="w-[24px]"><div class="w-full "><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 114 265" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>Bolt Design NYC Logo</title><path d="M38 0H0.5V208H76.5V265H114V56.5H38V0Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="col-start-7 col-end-13 lg:col-start-5 lg:col-end-7"><a class="block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=202+Banker+Street+Brooklyn+NY+11222"><p class="text-current font-body text-md">202 Banker Street</p><p class="text-current font-body text-md">Brooklyn, NY 11222</p></a></div><div class="col-span-6 lg:col-span-2"><a class="text-current font-body text-md block hover:text-yellow transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@bolt.build">hello@bolt.build</a><a class="t